column10: Cars that are coming off the exit ramp from Fairfax County Parkway to go to Telegraph Road north are not allowed to turn right on red. But often many do. Additionally, while you have the white hand for priority to cross the crosswalk, many drivers will ignore this and go without looking. Use caution at this intersection.
